{{Infobox settlement |official_name = Ağbulaq |native_name = Մսմնա |pushpin_map = Republic of Artsakh |pushpin_mapsize = 300 |subdivision_type = De facto country |subdivision_name = {{flag|Republic of Artsakh}} |subdivision_type1 = De facto [[Administrative divisions of the Republic of Artsakh|region]] |subdivision_name1 = [[Martuni Region|Martuni]] |subdivision_type2 = De jure country |subdivision_name2 = {{flag|Azerbaijan}} |subdivision_type3 = De jure [[Administrative divisions of Azerbaijan|district]] |subdivision_name3 = [[Khojavend District|Khojavend]] |leader_title = |leader_name = |established_title = |established_date = |area_total_km2 = |area_footnotes = |population_as_of = 2005 |population_total = 71 |population_density_km2 = auto |timezone = [[Azerbaijan Time|AZT]] |utc_offset = +4 |timezone_DST = [[Azerbaijan Time|AZT]] |utc_offset_DST = +5 |coordinates = {{coord|39|44|41|N|46|54|52|E|region:{{xb|NKR}}|display=inline,title}} |elevation_m = |area_code = |website = }} '''Ağbulaq''' ({{lang-hy|Մսմնա|translit=Msmna}}; also: ''Mysmna'', ''Mysmana'', ''Momna'' and ''Masmına'') is a village in the [[Khojavend Rayon]] of [[Azerbaijan]] and [[Martuni Province]] of the [[Republic of Artsakh]].
